file.name: path-returns-typed-array.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0"
basePath: /api/v1
host: goat.example.com
info:
  title: Goat CRUD API
  version: 1.2.3
components:
  schemas:
    Goat:
      additionalProperties: false
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        birthday:
          type: string
          format: date
      type: object
paths:
  /goat/get-goats:
    get:
      consumes:
        - application/json
      description: Gotta get goats.
      produces:
        - application/json
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Goat'
      summary: Gotta get goats
